column7: Women Blue 2-Ply Protective Outdoor Mask
column14:
Pack of one 2-Ply cloth face mask
Color: Blue
Material: Cotton
How to use:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
Stretch the elastic string over your ears, making sure that the brand label is towards your right
Cover your nose & mouth and adjust so that no gaps are left
Avoid touching the mask while use and replace if it feels damp

Precaution:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
The mask is for individual use ONLY, not to be shared with others to prevent contamination

Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks

Disclaimer:
No mask can guarantee full protection from Covid-19
This mask can help avoid droplets and aerosol if used effectively as per the user instructions

One 2-Ply cloth face mask

This two-ply face mask lined with cotton jersey fabric was made keeping wearability and comfort in mind
This washable and reusable face mask with elasticated ear loops will protect you from harmful viruses

How to use:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
Stretch the elastic string over your ears, making sure that the brand label is towards your right
Cover your nose & mouth and adjust so that no gaps are left
Avoid touching the mask while use and replace if it feels damp

Precaution:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
The mask is for individual use ONLY, not to be shared with others to prevent contamination

Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks

Disclaimer:
No mask can guarantee full protection from Covid 19
This mask can help avoid droplets and aerosol if used effectively as per the user instructions

column14:
Unisex Pink & Black Embroidered Reusable 3-Ply Protective Outdoor Masks

3-Layered Filtration System
Protects from dust, pollution, bacteria & viruses
Special Features:
Comfortable breathing
Wider face coverage for maximum protection
Adjustable nose notch for enhanced protection
Soft, elastic ear loops for extra comfort
Minimal eyewear fogging
Low heat build up
Convenient flat-fold design for easy storage
Washable upto 30 washes 
Reusable
Accommodates all facial movements
Use Cases:
Outdoor walk, travel & commute, biking, cycling police, traffic, security & delivery personnel, school
How to Use:
Step 1: wash your hands before touching your mask
Step 2: when you put on the mask make sure it covers your nose and mouth and fits comfortably around your face
Step 3: while you have the mask on in public places, avoid touching it and replace it if it feels damp
Step 4: do not wear the mask for more than 6 hours continuously
Step 5: to remove the mask, remove it from behind, do not touch the mask; store away separately in a closed bin
Step 6: do not touch the front side of the mask
Step 7: wash mask with soap and water / antiseptic liquid after every use
Step 8: wash hands carefully with soap after removing mask
Precaution:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
The mask is for individual use ONLY, not to be shared with others to prevent contamination
Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks

Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask

Cover your nose & mouth and adjust so that no gaps are left
Avoid touching the mask while use and replace if it feels damp

The mask is for individual use ONLY, not to be shared with others to prevent contamination

Unisex Blue Printed 3-Ply Reusable Outdoor Masks

3 layered filtration system
Special Features:
Reusable
Washable
Foldable
Comfortable to wear
Use Cases:
Outdoor
How to use:
Step-1: Wash / sanitize your hands before touching the mask
Step-2: Wear the mask by holding ear straps only, do not touch the surface
Step-3: Pull the side straps and secure them behind the ears
Step-4: Mask should cover your mouth, nose, and chin and spread open the mask from the center
Step-5: Pemove the mask by using ear straps that do not touch the surface
Step-6: Wash the mask properly with disinfectant liquid after every use
Step-7: Wash / sanitize your hands after touching the mask
Precaution:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
The mask is for individual use ONLY, not to be shared with others to prevent contamination
Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks

column14:
Unisex 3Ply Protective Outdoor Face Masks
Special features:
Reusable
Washable
Soft, breathable fabric
Soft elastic ear loops for comfort
Use cases:
Outdoor

How To Use:
step-1: wash / sanitize your hands before touching the mask
step-2: wear the mask by holding ear straps only, do not touch the surface
step-3: pull the side straps and secure them behind the ears
step-4: mask should cover your mouth, nose, and chin and spread open the mask from the center
step-5: remove the mask by using ear straps that do not touch the surface
step 6: wash the mask properly with disinfectant liquid after every use
step-7: wash / sanitize your hands after touching the mask

Precaution:
Wash mask with soap and water / antiseptic liquid after every use
Wash hands carefully with soap after removing mask
Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks
Do not wear mask more than six hours continuously

Disclaimer:
No mask can guarantee full protection from Covid 19

column14:
Kazo Women Pack of 3 Blue & White Striped Single Layered Cloth Masks

Single Layered Filteration System

Special Features
Reusable
Washable
How To Use
Wash/ sanitize your hands before touching the mask
Wear the mask by holding ear straps only, do not touch the surface
Pull the side straps and secure them behind the ears
Mask should cover your mouth, nose, and chin and spread open the mask from the center
Remove the mask by using ear straps that do not touch the surface
Wash the mask properly with disinfectant liquid after every use
Wash / sanitize your hands after touching the mask

Precaution:
Always wash your hand with soap and water or sanitise them with alcohol rub before and after using the mask
The mask is for individual use ONLY, not to be shared with others to prevent contamination
Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks

column14:
Kazo Unisex 3-Ply Reusable Cloth Mask

3-Layer Filtration Mask

Special Features:
3 ply face mask lined with cotton jersey keeping the wearability and comfort in mind.
It is washable and re-usable with elasticated ear loops.
How to use:
Hold the mask using the ear stripes
Stretch adequate to the size of your face and fasten them over your ears
Ensure maximum coverage over the face by pulling the mask appropriately to cover your face specially the chin area
Remove the mask by using ear straps that do not touch the surface
Wash the mask properly with disinfectant liquid after every use
Wash / sanitize your hands after touching the mask

Usage:
Outdoor

Precaution
Wash mask with soap and water / antiseptic liquid after every use
Wash hands carefully with soap after removing mask

Warning:
Usage instructions & precautions should be followed as recommended
Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks

column14:

3-Layer Filtration System

Special Features
Washable and resuable
Foldable
Soft elasticated ear loops

How To Use
Step-1: Wash / sanitize your hands before touching the mask
Step-2: Wear the mask by holding ear straps only, do not touch the surface
Step-3: Pull the side straps and secure them behind the ears
Step-4: Mask should cover your mouth, nose, and chin and spread open the mask from the center
Step-5: Remove the mask by using ear straps that do not touch the surface
Step-6: wash the mask properly with disinfectant liquid after every use
Precaution

Improper usage of the mask may cause health risks
